WEBVTT

00:02:28.280 --> 00:02:34.176
And yet again I let down my loved ones.

00:02:34.200 --> 00:02:39.856
I realized that I ended up growing
only to remain the same

00:02:39.880 --> 00:02:42.936
a lazy, weak and useless person.

00:02:42.960 --> 00:02:49.146
When I got married I felt,
the burden of family and society

00:02:49.146 --> 00:02:53.420
that I was carrying around
for so many years,

00:02:53.420 --> 00:02:55.830
was finally off my head.

00:02:56.920 --> 00:03:01.176
I left all work and gave
my all to the happiness of my family.